snippet.title: Rangers of Oblivion - Hunt the Ultimate Prey
snippet.description:
Download Rangers of Oblivion and join Malheim’s most feared faction, the Rangers. Create a legacy of monster-hunting mastery, defend the land of Malheim and explore an ever-changing, living, breathing fantasy world.

Official website: http://roo.gtarcade.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RangersOfOblivion/
